cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM. 

The paper proposes a method for remote sensing image scene classification using a CNN embedding. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories. The method involves learning to map input pairs to a feature space where intra-class inputs are close and inter-class inputs are separated by a margin, which is a metric learning problem (cs.AI, cs.IR). Finally, the experiments involve evaluating the classification performance on remote sensing image datasets, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) category.
